### Activity 4: Assessing Progress and Providing Feedback

Work individually to complete the following user story:

* As a participant, I want to assess my progress and provide feedback on my learning experience during Day 1.

## Acceptance Criteria

* It's done when you have completed the assessment checklist and provided feedback on your progress.

## 📝 Assessment Checklist

Please complete the following checklist to assess your progress:

- [ ] Understood the concepts of Hybrid Edge Cloud & edgeEngine.
- [ ] Familiarized yourself with the project's development tools and environments.
- [ ] Created a mimik developer account.
- [ ] Created an edge project.

## 📝 Progress Feedback Template

Use the template below to provide feedback on your progress:

### What I Learned:

(Describe key takeaways and what you learned today.)

### Challenges Faced:

(Describe any challenges you faced and how you overcame them.)

### Next Steps:

(Outline your goals and what you plan to focus on in the next session.)
\`\`\`

## 🏆 Bonus

If you have completed this activity, share your feedback:

* Discuss your progress and feedback with a partner or mentor.

Use your assessment and reflections to guide your conversation.

